OL,6,FThe former Sinn Finn leader says a BBC
OL,7,FSpotlight programme, and an
OL,8,Faccompanying online story, defamed him
OL,9,Fby alleging he sanctioned the killing
OL,10,Fof former Sinn Fein official Denis
OL,11,FDonaldson, for which he denies any
OL,12,Finvolvement.
OL,14,FMr Donaldson was shot dead in 2006,
OL,15,Fmonths after admitting his role as a
OL,16,Fpolice and MI5 agent for 20 years.
